Sanrio's Adorable, Rage-Filled New Character Aggretsuko Is All of Us 
It me. It you. By Leah Chernikoff Jan 6, 2017 This week, Sanrio, creator of Hello Kitty and so many other super cute characters, introduced a new member of the family: Aggretsuko. Sanrio Advertisement - Continue Reading Below Aggretsuko is a Red Panda who works as an office associate of a trading company in Tokyo. She is very #relatable. She introduces herself by her sign. Sanrio She has a brutal commute. Sanrio She gets dumped on and overworked by her bosses. Sanrio And subsequently burns with a rage so fierce it can only be released through metal karaoke. Sanrio
